text: Empress Dowager Wu may refer to: *Empress Wu (Zhaolie) (died 245), consort and empress dowager of the Shu Han state *Wu Zetian (624–705), consort and empress dowager of the Tang dynasty *Empress Wu (Song dynasty) (1115–1197), consort and empress dowager of the Song dynasty ==See also== *Empress Wu (disambiguation) Wu
title: Empress Dowager Wu
